titles.title: Tax Technical Corrections Act of 2014
Tax Technical Corrections Act of 2014
An original bill to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to make technical corrections, to remove provisions that are no longer applicable, and for other purposes.

action.text: Committee on Finance. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Wyden. With written report No. 113-155.

calendar.text: Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 367.
